## Styling Rules

- Use Tailwind classes; leverage DaisyUI components (e.g., `btn`, `input`).
- No inline styles; compose utilities instead.
- Respect theme via `data-theme` on the root container.
- Fonts and global CSS are imported from `src/assets/styles/index.css`.

## Shadow DOM Rules (content scripts)

- Render inside Shadow DOM using `createShadowRoot(styles)`.
- Inject styles via `adoptedStyleSheets` in production, or dev HMR flow.
- Use `:host` and `#my-ext` prefix-aware selectors.

### Content script boot (prod)

```tsx
import styles from '@assets/styles/index.css?inline';
import createShadowRoot from '@utils/createShadowRoot';

import Content from './Content';

const root = createShadowRoot(styles);
root.render(<Content />);
```
